    <item>
      <title>Hyde-X Tag Shortcode</title>
      <link>https://pyotek.github.io/news/hyde-x-tag-shortcode</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Aug 2016 02:02:02 +0200</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://pyotek.github.io/news/hyde-x-tag-shortcode</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Want to use tags (categories) in your .md files when using the Hyde-X theme like &lt;a class=&#34;label&#34; href=&#34;https://pyotek.github.io/categories/this&#34;&gt;this&lt;/a&gt;?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Then this line is for you:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-html&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;a class=&amp;quot;label&amp;quot; href=&amp;quot;{{ &amp;quot;/categories/&amp;quot; | absURL }}{{ .Get &amp;quot;txt&amp;quot; | urlize }}&amp;quot;&amp;gt;{{ .Get &amp;quot;txt&amp;quot; }}&amp;lt;/a&amp;gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Save in &lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;root&amp;gt;/static/shortcodes/tag.html&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Use it like &lt;code&gt;{{&amp;lt; tag txt=&amp;quot;this&amp;quot; &amp;gt;}}&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
